# Development Guide

## Local Development

1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

2. Run local development server:
   ```bash
   npm run serve --port=9000
   ```

3. Add to WeWeb Editor:
   - Open WeWeb editor
   - Open developer popup (click on profile picture)
   - Add localhost:9000 as custom element

## Build and Deploy

- Check for build errors:
  ```bash
  npm run build --name="ww-chat-ai" --type="element"
  ```

- Deploy to production:
  ```bash
  npm run deploy --name="ww-chat-ai" --type="element"
  ```

